{"tid":194048,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【令人心酸】報車禍新聞知道丈夫死咗 女主播強忍淚水完成工作","createTime":"2017-04-09T16:55:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-10T06:33:56.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a9ac2852bfdf40e31b125decc89b8c6f944adc7d","tid":194048,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T16:55:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170409/large/1491697526_4f0d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170409%2Flarge%2F1491697526_4f0d.jpg&h=a435ceec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n印度一名女主播在報道一宗車禍消息時，知悉其中一名死者是她的丈夫，但她仍保持記者的鎮定，直至新聞結束後才崩潰流淚。<br />\n28歲的卡雅(Supreet Kaur)在印度電視台IBC24當主播，她日前在報道一宗車禍突發消息，從受訪者提供的失事汽車車款、事發地點和時間等資料中，已猜到是丈夫的車出事。然而她冷靜地報道這宗新聞和其他新聞，直至10分鐘新聞結束才哭起來。<br />\n一位編輯說在她報新聞期間，他們已知道車禍死者包括她的丈夫，但沒有勇氣告訴她。他表示她有第六感知道丈夫出事，但待完成工作後才致電給親友。她的一位同事稱讚她勇敢，新聞部雖感到哀傷，但亦以她為傲。<br />\n卡雅與丈夫結婚只有一年，有一名年幼女兒。據說她丈夫的車被其他車從後猛撞，車內5人3死2重傷。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170409/56540289\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170409%2F56540289&d=%2BQAufOe15lwSrakhKFXs1tZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=2a90fb96\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170409%2F56540289&h=e4c5b6d3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170409/56540289</a>"},{"pid":"0958c6339b150a50e9f23117a372b427b3f49ccd","tid":194048,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T17:18:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8090b1bb264f5fc85065a89e3046dfa1c4800679","tid":194048,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T17:37:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"745acb746f005